timelineItems.text: FINAL: @FCDallas defends @RailHawksFC 5-2 in quarterfinals of #USOC2014. #FCDallas will host @PhilaUnion in semifinals.

timelineItems.name: FC Dallas
timelineItems.text: HAT TRICK HAT TRICK HAT TRICK!!!! @superraton7 with his 3rd on ANOTHER feed from Fabian Castillo! This one is over! FCD leads 5-2

timelineItems.name: RailHawksFC
timelineItems.text: FT RailHawks are defeated at home by FC Dallas 2-5.

timelineItems.name: FC Dallas
timelineItems.text: FULL TIME! @FCDallas ends @RailHawksFC's 23-match home unbeaten streak with a 5-2 win. FCD headed to the #USOC2014 semifinals! #DTID

timelineItems.comment: Second Half ends, Carolina RailHawks FC 2, FC Dallas 5.
